---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import LuvianMark from '@/components/LuvianMark.astro';

const lastUpdated = '2026-05-21';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Notice · Luvian Data Room"
  description="How Luvian Labs LLC handles personal information collected through the investor data room."
  showChrome={false}
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-ink-50/30 px-4 py-10 sm:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl">
      <div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 group">
          <LuvianMark size="md" />
          <div>
            <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink-900 group-hover:text-accent-dark">Luvian Labs LLC</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-ink-500">Investor data room — Privacy notice</div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>

      <article class="card max-w-none text-ink-800">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink-900">Privacy notice</h1>
        <p class="mb-4 text-xs text-ink-500">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

        <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-ink-200">
          Luvian Labs LLC (a Delaware single-member limited liability company,
          sole member Stephan Claxton; <em>"Luvian," "we," "us"</em>) operates this
          investor data room. This notice explains what personal information we
          collect when you use the data room, how we use it, who we share it
          with, and the choices you have.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-ink-900">1. Information we collect</h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-ink-700">
          <li>
            <strong>Identification you provide</strong> when you complete the
            confidentiality acknowledgment: your full legal name, your firm or
            organization (if any), and your email address.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Acknowledgment metadata</strong> generated automatically when
            you submit the form: the timestamp of your acknowledgment, your
            source IP address, your user-agent string, and the referring URL (if
            any).
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Server logs</strong> generated by our hosting provider
            (Vercel Inc.): timestamps, request paths, response status codes, and
            IP addresses, retained for the period and on the terms set by Vercel.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Authentication cookies</strong>: two HttpOnly, SameSite=Lax,
            HMAC-signed cookies — one proves you entered the correct access code,
            the other records that you accepted these terms. Both expire after
            the period set by the
            <code>INVESTOR_ROOM_COOKIE_TTL</code> environment variable (default
            seven days). The cookies do not contain any of your information in
            plaintext other than the values you provided to us.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ink-700">
          We do not use third-party analytics, advertising trackers, fingerprinting,
          or session-replay tools on this data room.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-ink-900">2. How we use it</h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-ink-700">
          <li>
            To authenticate you and gate access to confidential materials.
          </li>
          <li>
            To maintain an <strong>audit trail</strong> of who accepted the
            confidentiality acknowledgment and when, so that we can enforce its
            terms.
          </li>
          <li>
            To <strong>respond to you</strong> if you contact us, and to follow up
            with you about a potential investment or commercial relationship if
            that is the context in which you accessed the data room.
          </li>
          <li>
            To <strong>protect the security</strong> of the site, detect abuse,
            and comply with applicable law.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-ink-900">3. Who we share it with</h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-ink-700">
          <li>
            <strong>Vercel Inc.</strong> hosts the site and processes your request
            traffic; their privacy policy is available at
            <a class="underline" href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" rel="noopener" target="_blank">vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy</a>.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Our advisors</strong> (legal, tax, and finance) on a
            need-to-know basis, under professional or contractual obligations of
            confidentiality.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Acquirers or investors</strong> of Luvian Labs LLC in a due
            diligence, financing, or M&amp;A process, on a need-to-know basis and
            subject to confidentiality.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>As required by law</strong> — for example, in response to a
            valid subpoena, court order, or other legal process.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ink-700">
          We do <strong>not</strong> sell or rent your personal information, and
          we do not share it with advertising networks.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-ink-900">4. Retention</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-700">
          We retain acknowledgment records for as long as we have a legitimate
          business need (typically while the investment opportunity is open and
          for a reasonable period after) or as required by law. Authentication
          cookies expire automatically. Server logs follow our hosting provider's
          retention defaults.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-ink-900">5. Your choices</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-700">
          You can request that we delete your acknowledgment record, or that we
          provide you a copy of the personal information we hold about you, by
          emailing
          <a class="underline" href="mailto:stephan@luvian.info">stephan@luvian.info</a>.
          You can also clear your cookies or sign out at any time using the
          "Lock data room" button in the footer.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-ink-900">6. Children</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-700">
          This data room is not directed to children, and we do not knowingly
          collect personal information from anyone under 18.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-ink-900">7. Changes</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-700">
          If we change this notice we will update the "Last updated" date at the
          top. Material changes will be communicated to active investors by
          email.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-ink-900">8. Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-700">
          Stephan Claxton, Sole Member, Luvian Labs LLC ·
          <a class="underline" href="mailto:stephan@luvian.info">stephan@luvian.info</a>
        </p>
      </article>

      <div class="mt-6 text-center text-xs text-ink-500">
        <a href="/" class="text-accent-dark underline">Return to data room</a>
        · © {new Date().getFullYear()} Luvian Labs LLC
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
